title: Human Events Daily - Oct 15 2021 - H.E. + Rasmussen Poll Shows Concerns over Supply Chain Disruption
description:
Exclusive Human Events + Rasmussen polls shows Americans are deeply concerned about supply chain disruptions, the Chicago police force is facing a 50% reduction in cops on patrol due to coronavirus vaccine mandates, new pentagon report reveals that suicide has killed more soldiers in three months than Covid has since the beginning of the pandemic, and Kavanaugh and Kagan clash over the Boston Bomber case. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
